2026-05-16T19:45:44.8435916Z 273            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-16T19:45:44.8436176Z 274            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-16T19:45:44.8436345Z 275            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-16T19:45:44.8436636Z 276            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-16T19:45:44.8436894Z 277            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-16T19:45:44.8437139Z 278            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
